hadiths[98]{hadithnumber,text}:
4268,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey shikar key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : jab to apna kutta (shikar key peechhey) chodey to Allah Taala ka naam ley kar chhod, phir agar to shikar ko is haal mein pa ley ke kuttey ney usey qatl nahin kiya to Allah ka naam ley kar usey zibeh kar ley. aur agar shikar ko is haal mein paey ke kutta usey qatl kar chuka hai lekin us ney kuchh nahin khaya to wo shikar to kha sakta hai kyonkey us ney usey terey liye pakda hai aur agar to dekhey ke kuttey ney is mein sey kuchh kha liya hai to to is mein sey kuchh bhi na kha kyonkey kuttey ney to usey apney liye pakda hai. aur agar terey kuttey key sath aur kuttey bhi mil jaeyn, phir wo mil kar kisi janwer ko qatl kar den, phir chahey wo usey na bhi khaeyn to bhi to us sey kuchh na kha kyonkey tujhey ilm nahin ke un mein sey kis kuttey ney usey qatl kiya hai?"
4269,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mea'raaz teer key shikar key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jo janwer to teer ki nauk sey shikar kerey. wo to kha ley aur jo janwer uskey pehlu sey shikar karey (woh na kha kyonkey) wo chot sey mara hai. mainey aap sey kuttey (key shikar) key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jab to apna kutta chodey aur wo janwer ko ja pakdey lekin khud na khaye to to usey kha sakta hai kyonkey kuttey ka pakadnaa bhi zibeh hi hai. aur agar terey kuttey key sath koi aur kutta mil jaey aur tujhey khatra ho ke shayad uskey sath us ney bhi pakda hai aur maar diya hai to to na kha kyonkey tu ney apney kuttey ko chhodtey waqt بسم اللہ padhi hai, dusrey kuttey par nahin."
4270,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha ke main apna sadhaayaa huwa kutta shikar par chhodta hun, wo usey pakad ley to? aap ney farmaya : jab to apna sadhaayaa huwa kutta chodey aur بسم اللہ bhi padhey, phir wo pakad ley to to kha sakta hai. mainey kaha : agar-che wo qatl kar dey? aap ney farmaya : agar-che qatl kar dey. mainey kaha : main mea'raaz teer chalata hun to phir? aap ney farmaya : agar wo nauk key bal lagey to to kha sakta hai aur agar wo kisi aur janib sey lagey to phir na kha."
4271,"Hazrat Abu Sa'alba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum shikar waley ilaqey mein rehtey hain. main teer sey bhi shikar karta hun, apney sadhaaey huye aur un sadhaaey kutton key sath bhi. aap ney farmaya : jo to apney teer sey shikar kerey. usey kha sakta hai ba-sharte-ke tuney (chhodtey waqt) بسم اللہ padhi ho. isi tarah jo shikar sadhaaey huye kuttey sey kerey. wo bhi kha sakta hai ba-sharte-ke tu ney kutta chhodtey waqt بسم اللہ padhi ho, albatta jo shikar to un sadhaaey (ghair tarbiyat yafta) kuttey sey kerey. agar us ko apney haath sey zibeh kerey. tab kha sakta hai."
4272,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Taai) (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney sadhaaey huye kuttey shikar par chhodta hun. wo shikar ko merey liye pakad kar rakhtey hain to kya main kha sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : jab to sadhaaey huye kuttey chodey aur wo terey liye shikar pakdey rakhen (khud na khaeyn) to kha ley. mainey kaha : agar wo qatl kar den to? aap ney farmaya : chahey (chaahey) qatl kar den, albatta unkey sath koi aur kutta shareek na ho. mainey kaha ke main mea'raaz teer phainktaa hun jo shikar ko phaad deta hai? aap ney farmaya : agar to teer phaad dey to kha ley lekin agar wo janwer ko nauk ki bajaey kisi aur jagah sey lagey to na kha."
4273,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey shikar key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : jab to apney (sadhaaey huye) kuttey ko chhodey, phir uskey sath aur kuttey mil jaeyn jin par Allah Taala ka naam na liya gaya ho to usey na kha kyonkey to nahin janta ke un mein sey kis kuttey ney qatl kiya hai?"
4274,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kuttey key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : jab to apna kutta chhodey, بسم اللہ padhey to us ka shikar kha ley. aur agar to apney kuttey key sath koi aur kutta paey to phir na kha kyonkey tu ney apney kuttey par بسم اللہ padhi thi na ke dusrey par."
4275,"Hazrat Shaabi ney kaha ke Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke Nahreen shehar mein hamarey padosi they, milney julney waley aur Allah-log (Zahid) aadmi they, ney farmaya ke mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha ke main apna kutta shikar par chhodta hun, phir apney kuttey key sath koi aur kutta paata hun. main nahin janta ke un mein sey kis ney shikar pakda hai? aap ney farmaya : to na kha kyonkey tu ney sirf apney kuttey par بسم اللہ padhi thi na ke dusrey par."
4276,Hazrat Shaabi bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Adi (Raziallahu anhu) sey usi qisam ki riwayat aati hai.
4277,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya, mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha ke main shikar key liye apna kutta chhodta hun. aap ney farmaya : jab to apna kutta chhodey aur بسم اللہ padhey to us ka shikar kha sakta hai. agar kutta is mein sey kuchh kha ley to phir to na kha kyonkey us ney wo shikar apney liye pakda hai. aur jab to apna kutta chhodey, phir uskey sath koi aur kutta paey to us ka shikar na kha kyonkey tu ney sirf apney kuttey par بسم اللہ padhi hai na ke dusrey par."
4278,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : main apna kutta chhodta hun, phir apney kuttey key sath koi aur kutta bhi paata hun. main nahin janta ke un mein sey kis ney shikar pakda hai? aap ney farmaya : na kha kyonkey tu ney sirf apney kuttey par Allah ka naam liya hai dusrey par nahin."
4279,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mea'raaz key teer key shikar key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : jisey teer nauk key bal laga ho, usey kha ley aur jisey arz key bal (ya kisi aur taraf sey) laga ho, wo chot sey marney wala janwer hai. mainey aap sey shikari kuttey key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : jab to kutta chhodey aur Allah ka naam ley to us ka shikar kha ley. mainey kaha : agar wo qatl kar dey? aap ney farmaya : chahey wo qatl kar dey. lekin agar wo is mein sey khaney lagey to phir na kha. aur agar to uskey sath koi aur kutta paey jabkey janwer khatam ho chuka ho to usey na kha kyonkey tu ney Allah ka naam sirf apney kuttey par liya hai na ke dusrey kuttey par."
4280,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey shikar key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jab to apna kutta chhodey aur us par بسم اللہ padhey, phir wo qatl bhi kar dey lekin khud na khaye to wo shikar to kha ley. aur agar wo khana shuru kar dey to phir na kha kyonkey (is sey malum hota hai ke) us ney shikar apney liye pakda hai na ke terey liye."
4281,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Hazrat Jibril (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bataya : … lekin hum kisi aisey ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein kutta ya tasweer ho. us din aap ney subah key waqt kuttey maarney ka hukm diya yahan tak ke aap chhotey chhotey kuttey maarney ka bhi hukm detey they.
4282,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mustashnaa shuda kutton key ilawa kutton ko maarney ka hukm diya.
4283,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Umar) (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko buland aawaz key sath kutton key qatl ka hukm detey suna, phir kuttey maarey jatey they magar shikari ya janweron (aur kheton) ki hifazat ki khatir rakhey huye kutton ko qatl nahin kiya jata tha."
4284,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney shikari aur janweron (ya kheton ) ki hifazat key liye rakhey gaey kutton key ilawa dusrey kuttey maarney ka hukm diya.
4285,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye baat na hoti ke kuttey bhi eik makhluq hain to main un sab key qatl ka hukm deta. ab tum khalis siyah kuttey ko qatl karo. jo log bhi aisa kutta rakhen jo na to kheti ya janweron ki hifazat key liye ho aur na shikar key liye to un ki nekiyon sey har roz eik qeeraat ki kami hoti rahegi.
4286,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein tasweer ya kutta ya junbi (sambhog ke bad napaki ki halat mein insan) ho.
4287,Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein kutta ya tasweer ho.
4288,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan farmaya ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) badey dukhi sey they. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aaj subah sey aap ki haalat ajeeb si mehsus ho rahi hai. aap ney farmaya : Jibril ney mujh sey aaj raat milney ka wada kiya tha lekin wo miley nahin. Allah ki qism ! unhoney kabhi mujh sey wada khilafi nahin ki. aap sara din isi tarah rahey, phir aap ko khayal aaya ke hamari bistaron wali charpai key nichey kuttey ka eik pilla betha hai. aap ney hukm diya aur usey nikal diya gaya, phir aap ney apney daste-mubarak sey wahan kuchh pani chhidak diya. jab Sham hui to Jibril alehissalam aap sey miley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein farmaya : aap ney to mujh sey wada kiya tha ke guzishta raat mujh sey milengey? wo kehney lagey : han, lekin hum kisi aisey ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein kutta ya tasweer ho. us din sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kutton key qatl ka hukm dey diya."
4289,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kutta rakhey, uskey sawab sey har roz do qeeraat kam kiye jaeyngey, siwaye iske wo shikari ho ya janweron ki hifazat key liye rakha gaya ho."
4290,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid bayan kartey hain ke hamarey paas Sufiyan bin Abu-Zuhair Shanaai (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur farmaney lagey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney aisa kutta rakha jo na kheti ki hifazat karta ho aur na janweron ki (aur na wo shikari ho) to uskey amal sey har roz eik qeeraat sawab kam kya jaeyga. mainey kaha : aey Sufiyan ! kya aap ney ye farman Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai? unhoney farmaya : han, is masjid key Rab ki qism !"
4291,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs shikar ya janweron key liye kuttey key ilawa kutta rakhey to uskey sawab sey har roz do qeeraat kam kiye jaeyngey.
4292,"Hazrat Salim sey walid mohtaram (Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma) sey manqul sey ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney shikar ya janweron (aur kheti ) key kuttey key ilawa kutta rakha, uskey sawab sey har roz do qeeraat kam kiye jaeyngey."
4293,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney kutta rakha jo na shikari ho aur na janweron ya kheti ki hifazat key liye ho to uskey sawab sey har roz eik qeeraat ki kami hoti rahegi.
4294,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney shikar ya kheti ya janweron key kuttey key ilawa koi kutta rakha, uskey aamale-sualeha sey har roz eik qeeraat ki kami hoti rahegi."
4295,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs aisa kutta rakhey jo na shikari ho aur na janweron ya kheti ki hifazat key liye ho, uskey sawab sey har roz do qirat kam hotey rahengey."
4296,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney janweron ki hifazat ya shikar karney waley kuttey key ilawa kutta rakha, uskey nek aamal sey har roz eik qeeraat ki kami ki jaeygi. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye alfaz bhi bayan farmaai ke kheti ki hifazat wala kutta bhi rakh sakta hai."
4297,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey ki qeemat, zaaniya ki ujrat aur kaahin ki sheerni (mithaai) (nazar aur niyaz) sey mana farmaya hai."
4298,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kuttey ki qeemat, kaahin ki nazar aur niaz aur zaaniya ki ujrat halal nahin."
4299,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zaaniya ki ujrat , kuttey ki qeemat aur hajjaam ki kamai bahut buri kamai hai."
4300,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney billi aur kuttey ki qeemat sey mana farmaya hai magar shikari kuttey ki qeemat li ja sakti hai. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke Hujjaaj ki Hammad bin Salma sey marwi (bayan karda) riwayat sahih nahin.
4301,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas sadhaaey huye kuttey hain. mujhey unkey barey mein bataaiye? aap ney farmaya : jo janwer wo terey liye pakad rakhen, to kha sakta hai. mainey kaha : agar-che wo usey qatl kar den? aap ney farmaya : chahey wo usey qatl kar den. us aadmi ney kaha : mujhey merey teer kamaan key barey mein bataaiye? aap ney farmaya : tera teer jo kuchh shikar kerey. wo to kha sakta hai. us ney kaha : agar-che wo shikar mujh sey ghaaieb ho jaey? aap ney farmaya : agar-che wo tujh sey ghaaieb ho jaey. jab tak to is mein apney teer key ilawa kisi aur teer ka nishan na paey ya wo badboodaar na ho jaey. ibne Sawaa' ney kaha : mainey ye hadees (jis tarah Saeed key wastey sey suni hai, isi tarah wastey key baghair, baraahe-raast bhi) Abu-Malik Ubedullah bin Akhnas sey suni hai."
4302,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke hum eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tahaama key Zul-Hulefa mein they. logon ko kuchh oont aur bakriyan milin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon key aakhir mein they. lashkar key ibtidaai logon ney jaldi kartey huye un janweron ko zibeh kiya aur haandiyaan (ya degen) chadha dein. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas pahunchey to aap ney hukm diya ke degen ulat di jaeyn, phir aap ney ghanimat un mein taqseem farmaee aur das bakriyon ko eik oont key barabar qarar diya. us doran main eik oont bhag khada huwa. logon key paas bahut kam ghodey they. logon ney us ko pakadney ki koshish ki lekin wo qabu na aa saka. eik aadmi ney us ko teer maara to wo ruk gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : in gharelu janweron mein bhi baaz kabhi kabhi wehshi ban jatey (jangli janweron ki tarah insanon sey bhagney lagtey) hain, lihaza agar koi janwer qabu na aaye to tum us sey yehi sulook karo."
4303,Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey shikar key barey mein puchha to aap ney irshad farmaya : jab to teer chalaey to بسم اللہ padh ley. agar wo teer janwer ko qatl bhi kar dey to bhi kha ley siwaey iske ke to usey pani mein gira huwa paey tujhey kya ilm ke usey pani ney maara hai ya terey teer ney?
4304,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey shikar key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jab tu بسم اللہ padh kar apna teer chalaey ya kutta chhodey aur tera teer (shikar ko) qatl kar dey to to shikar kha sakta hai. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar wo shikar mujh sey eik raat tak ghaaieb raha to? aap ney farmaya : agar to us janwer mein apna teer pa ley aur uskey ilawa kisi aur zakham ka nishan na ho to usey kha sakta hai, albatta agar wo pani mein gir gaya (aur mar gaya) ho to usey mat kha."
4305,Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum shikari log hain. kabhi hum mein sey koi shakhs shikar par teer chalata hai aur wo (shikar) us sey eik do raaten ghaaieb rehta hai. shikari uski khoj lagata huwa pahunchta hai to usey be-jaan paata hai jabkey us ka teer is mein pewast hota hai? aap ney farmaya : jab to apna teer is mein laga huwa pehchan ley aur janwer mein kisi darindey key zakham laganey ka koi nishan na ho aur tujhey yaqin ho ke terey teer hi ney usey qatl kiya hai to to usey kha sakta hai.
4306,Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to apna teer is mein laga huwa pehchan ley aur koi doosra nishan is mein na ho aur tujhey yaqin ho ke terey teer hi ney usey qatl kiya hai to to usey kha sakta hai.
4307,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main shikar ko teer maarta hun, phir is ki khoj lagatey huye eik raat key baad usey paata hun (to kya karun?) aap ney farmaya : jab to is mein apna teer pehchan ley. to usey kha sakta hai ba-sharte-ke kisi darindey ney is mein sey kuchh na khaya ho."
4308,Hazrat Sa'alba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney shikar ko teen din baad bhi pa ley to usey kha sakta hai siwaey iske ke wo badboodaar ho jaey.
4309,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey arz kiya : usey Allah key Rasool ! main apna kutta chhodta hun, wo kisi shikar ko pakad leta hai lekin main koi aisi chiz nahin paata jis key sath usey zibeh kar sakun to main kisi tez dhaar patthar ya lakdi sey usey zibeh kar leta hun (to kya ye durust hai)? aap ney farmaya : khoon baha jis chiz sey bhi ho sakey. (aur zibeh kartey waqt) Allah Taala ka naam ley."
4310,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main sadhaaey huye kuttey shikar par chhodta hun aur wo usey merey liye pakade rakhtey hain to kya main usey kha liya karun? aap ney farmaya : jab to sadhaaey huye kuttey Allah ka naam ley kar chhodey aur wo shikar ko terey liye pakade rakhen (khud na khaeyn) to to usey kha sakta hai. mainey kaha : chahey chahey usey qatl kar dein? aap ney farmaya : chahey chaahey qatl kar dein ba-sharte-ke unkey sath koi aur kutta shareek na ho. mainey kaha : main mea'raaz teer phainktaa hun aur koi janwer shikar karta hun to kya usey kha sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : jab to mea'raaz teer phenkey aur بسم اللہ padhey, phir wo teer shikar ko nauk key sath phaadey to usey kha sakta hai. aur agar wo teer chaudai key bal ja kar lagey to phir usey na kha."
4311,Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mea'raaz teer key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jab wo janwer ko nauk key bal lagey to usey kha sakta hai aur jab wo arz key bal lagey aur janwer ko qatl kar dey to wo chot sey mara hai. usey mat kha.
4312,Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mea'raaz key shikar key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jab wo nauk key bal lagey to shikar kha ley aur jab arz key bal lagey to mat kha.
4313,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mea'raaz key shikar key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jis janwer ko to uski nauk sey shikar kerey. usey to kha ley aur jis janwer ko wo arz key bal lagey, wo chot sey marney wala janwer hai."
4314,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sehra mein rahega, sakht tabiyat ho jaeyga. aur jo shakhs shikar key peechhey lag gaya, wo (har chiz sey) ghafil ho gaya. aur jo shakhs badshah ka dum0chhalla bana, wo aazmaaish mein pad gaya. alfaz ibne Musannaa key hain."
4315,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik erabi (dehati) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas khargosh bhoon kar laya aur aap key aagey rakh diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney haath na badhaya aur na khaya lekin aap ney logon sey farmaya ke khaeyn. erabi (dehati) ney bhi na khaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey puchha : to kyon nahin khata? us ney kaha : main har mahiney sey teen din roza rakhta hun (aaj mera roza hai). aap ney farmaya : agar tu ney nafl rozey rakhney hon to chaandni raaton key rozey rakha kar.
4316,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik dafa farmaya : qaaha key din hamarey sath kon hazir tha? Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : main, wahan Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik khargosh laya gaya. laney waley shakhs ney ye bhi kaha ke mainey isey haiz aatey dekha hai. mera khayal hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey na khaya, phir aap ney (haazirin sey) kaha : tum khao. wo aadmi kehney laga : mera roza hai. aap ney farmaya : kaisa roza? us ney kaha : har mahiney sey teen rozey. aap ney farmaya : phir to chaandni raaton tehra, chaudah aur pandarah taareekh key kyon nahin rakhta?"
4317,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke maqame-marruz-zohraan mein hum eik khargosh key peechhey bhagey. mainey usey pakad liya aur usey ley kar Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya. unhoney usey zibeh kiya, phir uski chaaron taangein mujhey dey kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja. aap ney unhein qubul farma liya."
4318,"Hazrat ibne Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey do khargosh shikar kiye lekin mujhey koi aisi chiz na mil saki jis sey main unhein zibeh kar sakta to mainey unhein eik tez dhaar patthar sey zibeh kar diya, phir mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is barey mein puchha to aap ney mujhey unkey khaney ka hukm diya (khaney ki ijazat di)."
4319,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif farma they ke aap sey saandey key barey mein puchha gaya. aap ney farmaya : main na to usey khata hun na haram kehta hun.
4320,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! saandey key barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? aap ney farmaya : na main usey khata hun na haram karta hun.
4321,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik bhuna huwa goh laya gaya aur aap ko pesh kiya gaya. aap ney usey khaney key liye haath badhaya ke haazirin mein sey kisi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye goh ka gosht hai. aap ney apna haath rok liya. Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya goh haram hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin. lekin ye meri qom key ilaqey (merey watan) main nahin paya jata, is liye mujhey is sey kuch karaahat si mehsus hoti hai. Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) goh ki taraf badhey aur us sey khaya jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) dekh rahey they."
4322,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (aap ki zauja mohtarma) Hazrat Memuna binte Haris (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan gaya. wo meri khaala thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein saandey ka gosht pesh kiya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us waqt tak koi chiz nahin khatey they, jab tak pata na chal jata ke ye kya hai? is liye eik aurat ney kaha : tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bata kyon nahin detey ke aap kya khaney lagey hain? phir us ney aap ko bata diya ke ye saandey ka gosht hai. aap ney usey chhod diya. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : kya ye haram hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin. lekin ye meri qom key ilaqey (merey watan) main nahin paya jata, is liye mujhey is sey kuchh karaahat si mehsus hoti hai. Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey bartan apni taraf khinch liya aur usey kha liya jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey (khatey huye) dekh rahey they. aur (Yazid) ibne Asamm ney (ye riwayat apni khaala Ummul-Mominin) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey us (ibne-Shahab Imam Zohri (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ko bayan ki. aur wo (ibne Asamm) Hazrat Memuna ki parwarish mein they."
4323,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : meri khaala mohtarma ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko paneer, ghi aur saandey pesh kiye. aap ney paneer aur ghi to kha liya lekin saandey napasand kartey huye chhod diye (na khaye), albatta wo aap key dasterkhaan par khaye gaey. agar ye haram hotey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key dasterkhaan par na khaye jatey aur na aap unkey khaney ka hukm detey."
4324,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey saandey (ka gosht) khaney key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya ke Ummey Hufaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ghi, paneer aur saandey bhejey. aap ney ghi aur paneer to kha liye lekin saandey napasand kartey huye chhod diye. agar ye haram hotey to na aap key dasterkhaan par khaye jatey aur na aap unkey khaney ki ijazat detey."
4325,"Hazrat Sabit bin Yazid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. log eik manzil mein utrey to unhein bahut sey saandey mil gaey. mainey eik saandaa pakda, usey bhoonaa aur Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaya. aap ney eik lakdi pakdi aur uskey sath uski ungliyan ginney lagey, phir farmaya : Bani-Israel ki eik qom ko zamin key janweron ki shakal mein maskh kar diya gaya tha. main nahin janta ke wo kon sey janwer they? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! logon ney to isey kha bhi liya hai. lekin aap ney na to iskey khaney ka hukm diya aur na (is key khaney sey) roka."
4326,"Hazrat Sabit bin Wadeea' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik saandaa ley kar aaya. aap usey ulat palat kar dekhney lagey, phir farmaya : eik qom ki shakleyn bigaad di gaee thin, malum nahin us ka kya bana? mujhey malum nahin, shayad ye bhi unhi mein sey ho."
4327,"Hazrat Sabit bin Wadeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik aadmi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas goh ley kar aaya. aap ney farmaya : eik ummat ko maskh kar diya gaya tha, (ye un mein sey na ho) (wallahu-aalam)."
4328,Hazrat ibn Abi Ammaar sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey lagad-bigad key barey mein puchha to unhoney mujhey uskey khaney ko kaha. mainey kaha : kya wo shikar mein dakhil hai? unhoney farmaya : haan. mainey kaha : kya aap ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai. kehney lagey : haan.
4329,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har kuchli wala darinda haram hai.
4330,Hazrat Abu Sa'alba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney har kuchli waley darindey ko khaney sey mana farmaya hai.
4331,Hazrat Abu Sa'alba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : daakaa dalna halal nahin aur koi kuchli wala darinda bhi halal nahin. aur baandh kar nishaanon sey maara huwa janwer bhi halal nahin.
4332,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key din gadhon key gosht sey mana farmaya aur ghodon ka gosht khaney ki ijazat di.
4333,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein ghodey ka gosht khaney diya aur gadhey key gosht sey rok diya.
4334,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar ki jang key din hamein ghodey ka gosht khaney diya aur gadhey key gosht sey rok diya.
4335,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure mubarak mein ghodey ka gosht khaya kartey they.
4336,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ghodey , khachchar aur gadhey ka gosht khana jayez nahin."
4337,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghodey, khachchar, gadhey aur kuchli waley darindey ka gosht khaney sey mana farma diya."
4338,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum ghodey ka gosht khatey they. Ata (shagrid) ney kaha : khachchar ka bhi? farmaya : nahin.
4339,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwae-Khaibar key din nikahe-mut'aa aur gharelu gadhon key gosht sey mana farma diya tha.
4340,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key din aurton key sath nikahe-mut'aa karney aur gharelu gadhon ka gosht khaney sey rok diya tha.
4341,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key din gharelu gadhon sey mana farma diya tha.
4342,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey aisi hi hadees zikr farmaee hai magar is mein khaibar ka zikr nahin kiya.
4343,Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key din gharelu gadhon key gosht sey rok diya tha. bhuna huwa ya kachchaa.
4344,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hamney Khaibar key din basti sey bahar kuchh gadhey pakad liye aur unka salan pakaayaa, phir Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey eik aelan karney waley ney aelan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney gadhey key gosht ko haram qarar dey diya hai, lihaza gadhey key gosht wali haandiyaan ulat do. hamney ulta dein."
4345,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney subah key waqt khaibar par hamla kiya jabkey wo apni kudaleyn leykar (kaam kaaj key liye) hamari taraf aa rahey they. junhi unhoney hamein dekha, shor macha diya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur us ka lashkar aa gaya. aur wo mud kar qiley ki taraf bhagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (shukr aur dua ke liye) apney mubarak haath uthaey aur farmaya : Allahu-Akbar ! Allahu-Akbar ! khaibar tabah ho gaya. hum jab kisi qom key ilaqey mein aa dhamkatey hain to un daraaiye huye logon ka bahut bura haal hota hai. hamney wahan gadhey pakad liye aur in ko pakka liya to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key manadi ney aelan kartey huye kaha : Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool mukarram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tumhein gadhon key gosht sey roktey hain kyonkey wo paleed (haram) hain."
4346,Hazrat Abu Sa'alba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya : log jihad karney ki khatir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath khaibar ki taraf gaey. logon ko us waqt bahut bhook lagi thi. wahan logon ney gharelu gadhey paey to unhoney in ko zibeh kar liya. ye baat Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki gaee to aap ney Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ko hukm diya aur unhoney logon mein aelan kiya : khabrdar ! gharelu gadhon ka gosht kisi aisey shakhs key liye halal nahin jo meri risalat ki gawahi deta hai.
4347,Hazrat Abu Sa'alba (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney har kuchli waley darindey aur gharelu gadhon ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya hai.
4348,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hamney Khaibar key din ghodon aur jangli gadhon ka gosht khaya, albatta Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein gadhey ka gosht khaney sey mana farma diya."
4349,Hazrat Umair bin Salma Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa hum Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath rauhaa key kisi maqam par they. sab log Mohrim (aehram ki halat mein) they. unhoney eik zakhmi jangli gadhaa dekha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kuchh na kaho yahan tak ke us ko shikar karney wala aa jaey. thodi der baad Bahaz qabiley ka wo aadmi bhi aa gaya jisney usey zakhmi kiya tha. wo kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap is gadhey ka jo chahen kijiye ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke isey logon mein taqseem kar den.
4350,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey eik jangli gadhaa shikar kiya. main usey ley kar apney sathiyon key paas aaya. wo sab Mohrim (aehram ki halat mein) they. sirf main Mohrim (aehram ki halat mein) nahin tha. hum sab ney is mein sey kuchh gosht kha liya, phir hum eik dusrey sey kehney lagey : agar hum iskey barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochh lein (to behtar hai ). hamney aap sey puchha. aap ney farmaya : tum ney achchhaa kiya. phir farmaya : kya tumharey paas us ka kuchh gosht baqi hai? hamney kaha : ji haan ! aap ney farmaya : kuchh hamein bhi bhejo ! hamney aap ko bheja. aap ney usey khaya, halanke aap Mohrim (aehram ki halat mein) they."
4351,"Hazrat Zehdam sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas eik murgh laya gaya. eik shakhs eik taraf ko hat gaya (baqi log khaney lagey). Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : tujhey kya huwa? us ney kaha : mainey isey gandagi khatey dekha hai, is liye mujhey is sey nafrat ho gaee hai. to mainey qism kha li thi ke murgh ka gosht nahin khaaunga. Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : qarib aa kar kha kyonkey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko murgh khatey dekha hai, phir aap ney usey apni qism ka kaffara ada karney ko kaha."
4352,Hazrat Zehdam Jurmi sey riwayat hai ke hum Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bethey they ke unka khana pesh kiya gaya aur unkey khaney mein murgh ka gosht tha. haazirin mein banu Taimillah key qabiley mein sey eik surkh rang ka shakhs tha. aisey lagta tha jaisey wo ghulam ho. wo khaney key qarib na aaya. Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya (khaney key) qarib ho. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko murgh ka gosht khatey dekha hai.
4353,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key din panjey key sath shikar karney waley perindey aur kuchli waley darindey ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya.
4354,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs chidiyaa ya us sey bhi chhotey janwer ko nahaq qatl kerey. Allah Taala (qiyamat key din) us sey uskey barey mein puchheyga. puchha gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! us ka haq kya hai? aap ney farmaya : usey zibeh kar key khaye. us ka sar kaat kar na phenk dey.
4355,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney samandar key pani key barey mein farmaya : samandar ka pani taahir aur mutah'hir (pak aur pak karne wala) hai aur us ka janwer bila zibeh halal hai.
4356,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein (sahil samandar par) bheja. hum teen-sau aadmi they. hamney apna zaade-rah apni gardanon par uthaya huwa tha. wo bhi khatam ho gaya yahan tak ke hum mein sey har aadmi ko eik din main eik khajoor milti thi. un sey puchha gaya : aey Abu-Adbullah ! eik khajoor aadmi ka kya guzaaraa karti hogi? unhoney farmaya : jab khajuren bilkul khatam ho gaeen to hamein us eik khajoor ki bhi qadr malum hoti thi. hum sahil samandar par pahunchey to hamney nagahani wahan eik badi machhli dekhi jisey samandar ney bahar phenk diya tha. hamney is mein sey atthaara din khaya.
4357,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum teen-sau oont sawaron ko (sahil ki taraf) bheja. hamarey Ameer Hazrat Abu-Ubaida bin Jarraah they. hum Quraish key eik qafiley ki ghaat mein they. hum sahil par ja thehrey. hamein sakht bhook ka samna tha yahan tak ke hum pattey khaney lagey, phir samandar (ki lehron) ney eik aabi (pani ka) janwer (sahil par) phenk diya. us ko anbar kaha jata tha. hum us sey taqriban nisf (aadhe) maah khatey rahey. hamney uski charbi ko bhi khub istimal kiya to hamarey jism pehley ki tarah motey-taazey ho gaey. Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ney uski eik pasli ko khada kiya, phir lashkar mein sey sab sey ooncha oont aur sab sey lamba aadmi talash kiya. wo aadmi us oont par sawar ho kar pasli key nichey sey saaf guzar gaya. (isi safar ka waqia hai ke) phir log bhook mein mubtala huye to eik aadmi ney teen oont nahar (qurban) kiye, phir unhein bhook lagi to mazeed teen oont nahar kar diye, wo phir bhook ka shikar huye to usi ney mazeed teen oont nahar kiye, phir Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ney (bahaisiyat Ameer) usey rok diya. (raawi hadees) Sufiyan ney Abu-Zubair sey, unhoney Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya (unhoney farmaya ke jab hum Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas wapis pahunchey aur) hamney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (us key mutalliq) puchha. aap ney farmaya : kya tumharey paas us janwer ka kuchh gosht baqi hai? (Hazrat Jabir ney farmaya : ) hamney us aabi janwer ki aakhon sey bahut sey matkey charbi key nikaley. aur uski aankh key gadhey mein chaar aadmi baa-aasaani utar gaey. aur (isi safar ka waqia hai ke) Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) key paas eik khajuron ki thaili thi jis mein sey wo hamein mutthi mutthi diya kartey they, phir nobat eik eik khajoor tak aa gaee. jab khajuren bilkul khatam ho gaeen to (us waqt) hamein eik khajoor ki qadr aur qeemat malum hoti thi."
4358,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) key matehet eik lashkar mein bheja. hamarey safar ke khaney khatam ho gaey. hum eik machhli key paas sey guzrey jisey samandar ney (sahil par) phenk diya tha. hamney is mein sey khaney ka irada kiya to Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamein rok diya, phir khud hi kehney lagey : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key bhejey huye hain aur Allah Taala key raastey mein aaye hain, is liye kha lo. hum kaee din tak is mein sey khatey rahey. jab hum wapis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to hamney aap ko is baat ki ittila di. aap ney farmaya : agar tumharey paas kuchh gosht baqi hai to hamarey paas bhi bhejo."
4359,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) key sath bheja. hum teen-sau-das sey zayed they. aap ney hamein khajuron ki eik bori bator zaade-rah di thi. Hazrat Abu-Ubaida hamein rozaana eik eik mutthi khajuren detey they. jab hamney unhein taqriban khatam kar diya to wo hamein eik eik khajoor deney lagey yahan tak ke hum usey bachchon ki tarah choostey rehtey. ooper sey pani pi letey. jab khajuren bilkul khatam ho gaeen to eik khajoor ka na milna bhi hum ko mehsus hota tha yahan tak ke hum apni lathiyon sey darakhton key pattey jhaad letey aur unhein phaank letey, phir ooper sey pani pi letey yahan tak ke hamarey us lashkar ka naam hi patton wala lashkar rakh diya gaya, phir hum sahil par pahunchey to wahan tiley jaisa eik aabi (pani ka) janwer pada tha jisey anbar kaha jata tha. Hazrat Abu-Ubaida ney farmaya : ye mara huwa hai, lihaza isey na khao, phir khud hi kehney lagey : hum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki fauj hain aur Allah Taala key raastey mein ja rahey hain, phir hum laachaar bhi hain, isliye Allah ka naam ley kar khao. hamney kuchh to khaya, kuchh sukha liya. us janwer ki aankh key gadhey mein tehra aadmi (aaram sey) beth gaey, phir Hazrat Abu-Ubaida ney uski pasli li, phir eik motey unchey oont par paalaan kas kar (eik lamba tadangaa aadmi bitha kar) usey pasli key nichey sey guzaaraa to wo saaf guzar gaya. jab hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to aap ney farmaya : tum itney din kahan rukey rahey? hamney arz kiya : hum Quraish key tijaarati qaflon ko talash kartey rahey, phir hamney aap key samney us aabi janwer ka zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : wo rizq tha jo Allah Taala ney tumharey liye mohaiyya farmaya. kya tumharey paas us ka kuchh gosht hai? hamney kaha : ji haan."
4360,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik tabeeb ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney kisi dawaai mein maindak dalney ka zikr kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maindak key qatl sey mana farma diya.
4361,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya hum saat jangon mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath gaey. hum (aap key sath rehtey huye) tiddiyan khaya kartey they.
4362,Hazrat Abu Yaafur ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey tiddi ko qatl karney key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : main chhe jangon mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath hazir huwa. hum tiddiyan khaya kartey they.
4363,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik chewnti ney eik Nabi ko kaat liya to unhoney chewnti ki us puri aabaadi ko aag laganey ka hukm diya. unhein jala diya gaya. Allah Taala ney un ki taraf ""wahi"" farmaee ke tujhey eik chewnti ney kaat liya, tu ney Allah Taala ki tasbih karney wali makhluq ko halak kar diya."
4364,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey manqul hai ke (sabiqa (pichhley)) anbiya mein sey eik Nabi eik darkht key nichey thehrey. eik chewnti ney unhein kaat liya. unhoney hukm diya to unkey purey bil ko tamam chewntiyon samet jala diya gaya. Allah Taala ney un ki taraf ""wahi"" farmaee. kyon na aap ney sirf eik chewnti ko maara? (aakhir ye bhi to Allah Taala ki tasbih bayan karti hain.) aur Ash-as ney ibne Sirin sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey isi (sabiqa) hadees ki misl (tarah) bayan kiya. aur is mein ye alfaz ziyada hain : ( فَاِنَّھُنَّ یُسَبِّحْنَ ) bilashuba ye (chewntiyan Allah taala ki) tasbih bayan karti hain."
4365,usi qisam ki riwayat Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai magar wo marfooa nahin (balke unka apna qol hai).
